high_descs: walk over to the kitchen table
pick up the wine bottle off of the kitchen table
bring the wine bottle over to the fridge
place the wine bottle in the bottom part of the fridge to cool, then take it back out again
walk on over to kitchen table again
place the bottle on the left side of the table
anns.task_desc: cool a bottle of wine that was on the kitchen table

high_descs: Walk to your left to the round white table at the corner of the room.
Pick up the green bottle at the right side of the table.
Walk to the left, turn to the left  and then turn right to the to the fridge.
Open the fridge, put it in the fridge to the right of the pink bottle, close the fridge and wait for a few seconds before picking up the bottle again.
Walk to the right and go back to the white round table again.
Put the bottle on the left side of the table next to a green square bottle.
anns.task_desc: Put back a cold green bottle on the left side of the round white table.

high_descs: Go to your left to the table.
Pick up the wine bottle on the table.
Turn around and go to your right to the refrigerator.
Chill the wine bottle in the refrigerator.
Turn around and return to the table.
Placed the wine bottle on the table to the right of the hand soap.
anns.task_desc: Place chilled wine on the table.
